'''黎明蟹屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Matuta'''''}}）是[[短尾下目|短尾下目]]（[[螃蟹|螃蟹]]）[[饅頭蟹總科|饅頭蟹總科]][[黎明蟹科|黎明蟹科]]的一個屬<ref name="Grave">{{cite journal |journal = [[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year = 2009 |volume = Suppl. 21 |pages = 1–109 |title = A classification of living and fossil genera of decapod crustaceans |author = Sammy De Grave |author2 = N. Dean Pentcheff |author3 = Shane T. Ahyong |display-authors = et al. |url = http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |language = en |access-date = 2014-05-28 |archive-date = 2011-06-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110606064728/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref>。本屬過往還包括其他近似但難以歸類的物種，但隨着近年這些物種的近親的發現，現時均獨立出去成為各自一屬，例如：[[伊神蟹屬|伊神蟹屬]]<ref name=WoRMS_440349>{{cite WoRMS |author=P. Davie |year=2009 |title=''Izanami curtispina'' (Sakai, 1961) |id=440349 |accessdate=2013-03-21 }}</ref>。

黎明蟹屬的學名來自[[古羅馬|古羅馬]]象徵黎明的女神[[馬圖塔|馬圖塔]]。

==物種==
本屬包括以下六個物種<ref name=WoRMS_205501>{{cite WoRMS |author=P. Davie |year=2010 |title=''Matuta'' Weber, 1795 |id=205501 |accessdate=2010-12-06}}</ref>
*[[彭氏黎明蟹|彭氏黎明蟹]] ''Matuta banksi'' <small>Leach, 1817</small>
* ''[[Matuta_circulifera|Matuta circulifera]]'' <small>Miers, 1880</small>
*[[红线黎明蟹|红线黎明蟹]] ''Matuta planipes'' <small>Fabricius, 1798</small>
* ''[[Matuta_purnama|Matuta purnama]]'' <small>Lai & Galil, 2007</small>
*[[頑強黎明蟹|頑強黎明蟹]] ''Matuta victor'' <small>(Fabricius, 1781)</small>：又名[[勝利黎明蟹|勝利黎明蟹]]
* ''[[Matuta_victrix|Matuta victrix]]''

